		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Philada.</placeName> <date>April 23<hi rend="sup">rd</hi>. 1854</date></p>
				<p><addressee>A Hart Esq</addressee> Parnass</p>
				<p>Kaal Kadosh Mickve Israel</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Sir &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;  The undersigned members<lb/> of the &#8220;K K M I&#8221;&#44; do respectfully request you to call a<lb/> special meeting of the members of the Congregation on the<lb/> <date>30th</date> Inst &#8220;for the purpose of approving the action of the<lb/> Board of Adjunta in repealing the vote of Censure passed<lb/> on the <persName>Revd. Isaac Leeser</persName>&#44; and for the further purpose of<lb/> passing suitable resolutions &#38; making a suitable appro&#61;<lb/>&#61;priation in his favor in part <sic>acknowledgement</sic> of his<lb/> past services to said Congregation &#38; to assist him in<lb/> any future enterprise.&#8221;</p>
